the laying out, planting, maintenance and protection of trees, shrubs and grass margins in and beside roads."]}, "\r"]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Street lighting", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "article-44"}], ["44."]}, "—(1) Where the Department considers that any road should be illuminated or better illuminated, it may provide for—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-44-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the supply of electricity or other means of illumination by any person having power in that behalf;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-44-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the installation of such system of illumination (including lamps, lamp posts, cables, supports for cables and other materials and apparatus) as appears to the Department to be necessary for the purpose; and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-44-1-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the operation and maintenance of any system of illumination installed under this Article."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) Where the Department considers that it is in the public interest for a street or footpath to which the public has access to be illuminated or better illuminated, the powers of the Department under paragraph (1) shall be exercisable in relation to that street or footpath as if it were a road.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) The Department may alter or remove any system of illumination installed under paragraph (1) or (2).\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(4) The Department may provide for the operation and maintenance of any system of illumination installed under Article 24 of the Roads (Northern Ireland) Order 1980", {"a", [{"class", "LegCommentaryLink"}, {"href", "#commentary-c16867011"}, {"title", "View the commentary text for this item"}, {"id", "reference-c16867011"}], ["F28"]}, " and may alter or remove any such system.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(5) The Department may, on such terms and conditions as may be agreed between the Department and any other person, provide, in respect of land which the Department in the exercise of its street planning functions under the Private Streets (Northern Ireland) Order 1980", {"a", [{"class", "LegCommentaryLink"}, {"href", "#commentary-c16867021"}, {"title", "View the commentary text for this item"}, {"id", "reference-c16867021"}], ["F29"]}, " has determined shall be regarded for the purposes of Part III of that Order as being comprised in a street, for—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-44-5-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the supply of electricity or other means of illumination by any person having power in that behalf; and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-44-5-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the installation of a system of illumination (including lamps, lamp posts, cables, supports for cables and other materials and apparatus)."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(6) For the purposes of, or in connection with, the exercise of its functions under this Article, the Department may obtain from the owner or occupier of any land, on such terms and conditions as may be agreed between the Department and that person, the consent of that person for the Department—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-44-6-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["to install and keep installed on, under or over the land any lamps, lamp posts, cables, supports for cables or other materials or apparatus; and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-44-6-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["to have access to the land for the purpose of inspecting, repairing, altering, renewing or removing any thing so installed."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(7) The power to make a vesting order in respect of any land under Article 113 includes power to create and vest in the Department for the purposes of, or in connection with, the exercise of its functions under this Article new rights over land as well as to vest existing rights and, in particular to create and vest in the Department—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-44-7-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the right to install and keep installed on, under or over any land any lamps, lamp posts, cables, supports for cables or other materials and apparatus; and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-44-7-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the right to have access to the land for the purpose of inspecting, repairing, altering, renewing or removing anything so installed."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(8) In this Article—\r"]}, {"ul", [{"class", "LegTabbed LegUnorderedList"}], [{"li", [], [{"p", [{"class", "LegListTextStandard LegLevel3"}], ["“footpath” means a way over which the public have a right of way on foot only, not being a footway or other part of a road;\r"]}]}, {"li", [], [{"p", [{"class", "LegListTextStandard LegLevel3"}], ["“street” means any street, lane, square, court, alley or passage, not being a road.\r"]}]}]}, {"div", [{"class", "LegAnnotations"}], [{"div", [{"class", "LegCommentaryItem"}, {"id", "commentary-c16867011"}], [{"p", [{"class", "LegCommentaryPara"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegCommentaryType"}], [{"a", [{"href", "#reference-c16867011"}, {"title", "Go back to reference for this commentary item"}], ["F28"]}]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegCommentaryText"}], [{"a", [{"class", "LegCitation"}, {"title", "Go to item of legislation"}, {"rel", "cite"}, {"href", "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/nisi/1980"}], ["1980 NI 11"]}]}]}]}, {"div", [{"class", "LegCommentaryItem"}, {"id", "commentary-c16867021"}], [{"p", [{"class", "LegCommentaryPara"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegCommentaryType"}], [{"a", [{"href", "#reference-c16867021"}, {"title", "Go back to reference for this commentary item"}], ["F29"]}]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegCommentaryText"}], [{"a", [{"class", "LegCitation"}, {"title", "Go to item of legislation"}, {"rel", "cite"}, {"href", "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/nisi/1980"}], ["1980 NI 12"]}]}]}]}]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Drainage of roads", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "article-45"}], ["45."]}, "—(1) The Department may, in a road or in land adjacent to or adjoining a road—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-45-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["construct and lay road drains;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-45-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["construct and lay drains for the purpose of preventing surface water from flowing on to the road;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-45-1-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["erect barriers to divert surface water into or through any existing drain."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) The Department may—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-45-2-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["scour, cleanse and keep open road drains;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-45-2-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["scour, cleanse and keep open drains constructed and laid by the Department under paragraph (1)(b);"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-45-2-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["for the purpose of relieving the flooding of any road, scour, cleanse and keep open any other drain in land adjacent to or adjoining a road."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) The power under paragraph (1)—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-45-3-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["to construct and lay a drain; or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-45-3-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["to erect barriers to divert surface water into or through any existing drain,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["includes power to discharge water through that drain into any inland waters, whether natural or artificial, or any tidal waters.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(4) If the owner or occupier of any land suffers damage by reason of the exercise by the Department of any power under paragraph (1), (2) or (3), the Department shall pay compensation therefor.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(5) Any question as to whether compensation is payable under paragraph (4) or as to the amount of any compensation so payable shall be determined by the Lands Tribunal.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(6) For the purpose of draining a road or otherwise preventing surface water from flowing on to it, the Department may acquire by agreement or otherwise any drain, or any right of making or of use or other right in or respecting a drain (with or without any materials or things belonging thereto).\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(7) Any person who, before the acquisition of a drain under paragraph (6), has acquired a right to use the drain, shall be entitled to use it or any drain substituted for it, to the same extent as he would or might have done had the drain not been acquired by the Department.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(8) Article 113(1) and (2) and Schedule 7 shall apply where under paragraph (6) the Department acquires otherwise than by agreement any drain or any right.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(9) In this Article and Article 46—\r"]}, {"ul", [{"class", "LegTabbed LegUnorderedList"}], [{"li", [], [{"p", [{"class", "LegListTextStandard LegLevel3"}], ["“road drain” means a drain the principal purpose of which is to drain a road;\r"]}]}, {"li", [], [{"p", [{"class", "LegListTextStandard LegLevel3"}], ["“drain” includes a ditch, cut, culvert, soakaway, dyke or sluice.\r"]}]}]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Obstruction of, interference with, or discharge of material into, a road drain, etc.", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "article-46"}], ["46."]}, "—(1) Any person who, without the consent of the Department, obstructs or interferes with—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-46-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a road drain;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-46-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a drain constructed and laid by the Department under Article 45(1)(b); or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-46-1-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a barrier erected by the Department under Article 45(1)(c),"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["shall be guilty of an offence and liable on summary conviction to a fine not exceeding level 3 on the standard scale.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) Any person convicted of an offence under paragraph (1) shall within such period as the court may allow—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-46-2-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["remove the obstruction or interference; and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-46-2-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["make good any damage done by him to the drain or barrier;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["and if he fails to do so he shall be guilty of a further offence and be liable on summary conviction to a fine not exceeding one-tenth of level 3 on the standard scale for each day on which that failure continues.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) Where—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-46-3-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a person obstructs or interferes with a drain or barrier in contravention of paragraph (1); and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-46-3-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the Department considers that by reason of that obstruction or interference there is, or is likely to be, a danger to persons using the road,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["then (whether or not proceedings are instituted for an offence under paragraph (1)) the Department may carry out such works of repair or reinstatement as in the opinion of the Department are necessitated by reason of his action and recover from that person any expenses thereby reasonably incurred by it.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(4) Any person who, without the consent of the Department, discharges any solid or liquid matter into—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-46-4-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a road drain; or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-46-4-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a drain constructed and laid by the Department under Article 45(1)(b),"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["shall be guilty of an offence and liable on summary conviction to a fine not exceeding level 3 on the standard scale.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(5) Any person convicted of an offence under paragraph (4) in respect of any drain shall within such period as the court may allow—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-46-5-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["cease to discharge any solid or liquid matter into the drain;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-46-5-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["remove any pipe or other thing through or by means of which the discharge in question was made; and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-46-5-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["make good any damage done by him to the drain;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["and if he fails to do so he shall be guilty of a further offence and be liable on summary conviction to a fine not exceeding one-tenth of level 3 on the standard scale for each day on which that failure continues.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(6) Where—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-46-6-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a person discharges any solid or liquid matter into a drain in contravention of paragraph (4); and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-46-6-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the Department considers that it is in the public interest to exercise its powers under this paragraph,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["then (whether or not proceedings are instituted for an offence under paragraph (4)) the Department may—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "article-46-6-i"}], ["(i)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["carry out such works as in the opinion of the Department are necessary to prevent any further solid or liquid matter being discharged in contravention of paragraph (4); and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "article-46-6-ii"}], ["(ii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["recover from that person any expenses thereby reasonably incurred by it."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(7) Where a person—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-46-7-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["has been convicted of an offence under paragraph (1) and becomes liable to prosecution for an offence under paragraph (2); or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-46-7-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["has been convicted of an offence under paragraph (4) and becomes liable to prosecution for an offence under paragraph (5),"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["the Department may itself do any thing which he has failed to do and recover from that person any expenses thereby reasonably incurred by it.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(8) A consent under paragraph (1) or (4) may be given subject to such conditions as the Department thinks fit and in particular, but without prejudice to the generality of the foregoing, subject to conditions—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-46-8-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["regulating the place and manner in which any matter is to be discharged into a drain;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-46-8-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["prohibiting the discharge of specified matter into a drain or otherwise regulating the kinds of matter which may be discharged into a drain."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(9) Any person who—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-46-9-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["does anything mentioned in paragraph (1) or (4) in pursuance of a consent given under that paragraph; and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-46-9-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["fails to comply with any condition subject to which that consent was given,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["shall be guilty of an offence and liable on summary conviction to a fine not exceeding level 3 on the standard scale.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(10) Where it appears to the Department that a person has contravened paragraph (9), then (whether or not proceedings are instituted for an offence under that paragraph) the Department may—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-46-10-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["revoke the consent given to that person under paragraph (1) or (4);"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-46-10-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["carry out such works of repair or reinstatement as in the opinion of the Department are necessitated by reason of his action; and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-46-10-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["recover from that person any expenses thereby reasonably incurred by it."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(11) Any person aggrieved by—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-46-11-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the refusal of the Department to give its consent under paragraph (1) or (4); or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-46-11-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["any condition subject to which any such consent is given,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["may, within 21 days of receiving notice thereof, appeal to the planning appeals commission by notice in writing under this Article.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(12) Paragraphs (2) and (3) of Article 84 shall apply to an appeal under this Article as they apply to an appeal under that Article.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(13) Nothing in this Article applies to—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-46-13-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the discharge into a drain of surface water from a building adjoining a road by means of a gutter in the footway of the road; or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-46-13-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["anything done in relation to a drain by the owner thereof or by a person exercising a right preserved by Article 45(7)."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(14) In this Article “discharge” includes cause or permit to be discharged.\r"]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Filling in of roadside ditches", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "article-47"}], ["47."]}, "—(1) If it appears to the Department that a ditch on land adjacent to or adjoining a road constitutes a danger to users of the road, the Department may—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-47-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["if it considers the ditch unnecessary for drainage purposes and any occupier of the land known to the Department agrees in writing that it is unnecessary for those purposes, fill it in; or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-47-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["place in the ditch or in land adjacent to or adjoining it, such pipes as the Department considers necessary in substitution for the ditch, and thereafter fill it in."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) If the owner or occupier of any land suffers damage by reason of the exercise by the Department of any power under paragraph (1), the Department shall pay compensation therefor.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) Any question as to whether compensation is payable under this Article or as to the amount of any compensation so payable shall be determined by the Lands Tribunal.\r"]}, {"div", [{"class", "LegClearPblock"}], []}, {"h3", [{"class", "LegPblock"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegPblockTitle"}], ["Safety of roads", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitleFirst"}], ["Removal of fallen structures, trees, etc.", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "article-48"}], ["48."]}, "—(1) Where from any cause—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-48-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["any wall, fence or other structure (whether of the same kind as those mentioned or not) erected on land adjoining a road; or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-48-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["any tree, or branch or bough of a tree, growing on land adjoining a road or in a road,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["falls upon or across the road so as to cause danger or obstruction to persons or vehicles using the road, the Department may, without giving notice to the owner or occupier of the land or to any other person, effect the removal of that structure, tree, branch or bough.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) Anything removed from a road by the Department under paragraph (1) may be replaced by it upon the land on which it was erected or grew.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) Where the Department exercises its powers under paragraph (1), it may recover from the owner or occupier of the land any expenses thereby reasonably incurred by it.\r"]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Prevention of obstruction to view, etc.", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "article-49"}], ["49."]}, "  Where the Department considers it necessary, for the prevention of danger arising from obstruction—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-49-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["to traffic upon a road, or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-49-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["to the view of persons entering or using a road,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegText"}], ["to impose restrictions with respect to any land other than restrictions imposed by or under any other provision of this Order, the Department may serve a notice in accordance with Schedule 4.\r"]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Removal of potentially dangerous trees and hedges", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "article-50"}], ["50."]}, "  Where the Department is satisfied that any tree or hedge adjoining, adjacent to, or growing on a road—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-50-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["is dead, damaged, diseased or insecurely rooted and by reason of its condition is likely to cause danger to persons using the road;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-50-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["obstructs or interferes with the light from any public lamp;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-50-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["endangers or obstructs the passage of vehicles or pedestrians, or obstructs the view of drivers of vehicles; or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-50-d"}], ["(d)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["otherwise prejudices the safety or convenience of persons using the road or prejudices the road,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegText"}], ["the Department may serve a notice on the owner of the tree or hedge, or on the occupier of the land on which such tree or hedge is growing, requiring him to remove the tree or hedge or to lop the tree or cut back the hedge to such an extent as will remove the obstruction or remedy any other matter to which the notice relates.\r"]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Dangerous land adjoining roads", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "article-51"}], ["51."]}, "  If the Department is of the opinion—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-51-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["that a building, wall or other structure is in such a condition as to be dangerous to persons using a road;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-51-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["that there is in or on any land adjoining a road an unfenced or inadequately fenced source of danger to persons using the road; or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-51-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["that there is on any land adjoining a road any illumination which is a source of danger to persons using the road,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegText"}], ["the Department may serve a notice on the owner of the structure or the owner or occupier of the land requiring him to carry out such works of repair, protection, removal, alteration or enclosure as will obviate the danger.\r"]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Prevention of solid matter being washed on to roads", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "article-52"}], ["52."]}, "  The Department may serve a notice on the owner or occupier of any land adjoining a road, requiring him to construct and lay such drains, erect such barriers or embankments or do such other works as are necessary to prevent any solid matter from such land from falling upon, or being washed or carried on to, the road, or into any drain, sewer or gully therein, in such quantities as may cause danger or substantial inconvenience to users of the road, or choke up the drain, sewer or gully.\r"]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Prevention of water falling or flowing on to roads", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "article-53"}], ["53."]}, "—(1) The Department may serve a notice on the owner or occupier of any building adjoining a road requiring him—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-53-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["to erect or repair such gutters or downpipes on the building;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-53-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["to construct such gutters in the footway of the road; or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-53-1-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["to carry out such other works,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["as are necessary to prevent—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "article-53-1-i"}], ["(i)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["water from the roof or any other part of the building falling upon persons using the road;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "article-53-1-ii"}], ["(ii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["so far as is reasonably practicable, surface water from the building flowing on to, or over, the road."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) Every gutter in the footway of a road shall be so constructed and kept in such good condition and repair by the owner or occupier of any building served by the gutter that it does not constitute a danger or a nuisance to road users.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) The Department may serve a notice on the owner or occupier of any building adjoining a road requiring him to carry out such works in relation to a gutter serving that building as are necessary to comply with paragraph (2).\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(4) The Department may serve a notice on the owner or occupier of land adjoining a road, requiring him to do such works as are necessary to prevent, so far as is reasonably practicable, surface water from the land flowing onto or over the road.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(5) The following are hereby repealed, namely—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-53-5-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["section 142 of the Belfast Corporation Act 1845", {"a", [{"class", "LegCommentaryLink"}, {"href", "#commentary-c16867031"}, {"title", "View the commentary text for this item"}, {"id", "reference-c16867031"}], ["F30"]}, "; and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-53-5-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["any other transferred local provision imposing obligations on an owner or occupier of a building in relation to the construction, maintenance or repair of gutters serving the building in footways adjoining the building."]}, "\r"]}, {"div", [{"class", "LegAnnotations"}], [{"div", [{"class", "LegCommentaryItem"}, {"id", "commentary-c16867031"}], [{"p", [{"class", "LegCommentaryPara"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegCommentaryType"}], [{"a", [{"href", "#reference-c16867031"}, {"title", "Go back to reference for this commentary item"}], ["F30"]}]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegCommentaryText"}], ["1845 c. cxlii"]}]}]}]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Removal of barbed wire", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "article-54"}], ["54."]}, "—(1) Where on any land adjoining a road there is a fence made with barbed wire, or having barbed wire in it, and the wire is, in the opinion of the Department, likely to be a danger to persons or animals using the road, the Department may serve on the occupier of the land a notice requiring him to—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-54-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["remove the barbed wire; or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-54-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["carry out such works as are necessary to prevent the barbed wire from being a danger to persons or animals using the road."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) For the purposes of this Article “barbed wire” means any wire with spikes or jagged projections.\r"]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Removal of projections from buildings", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "article-55"}], ["55."]}, "—(1) The Department may serve a notice on the owner or occupier of any building requiring him to remove or alter any projection erected or placed against or in front of a building if the projection—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-55-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["is, or is likely to be, an obstruction to safe and convenient passage along any road; or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-55-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["is, by reason of its being insecurely fixed or of its defective construction or otherwise, a source of danger to persons or vehicles using the road."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) In this Article “projection” includes any projecting window, porch, canopy, awning, sign, sign post, sign iron, showboard, gate, door, bar, wall, fence or step, or any other obstruction or projection.\r"]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Doors, etc. opening onto road", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "article-56"}], ["56."]}, "—(1) A door, gate or bar shall not, except with the consent of the Department, be so erected on land adjoining a road as to open outwards onto the road.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) Where a door, gate or bar is erected in contravention of paragraph (1) the Department may serve a notice on the owner or occupier of the land requiring him to alter the door, gate or bar so that it does not open outwards onto the road.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) Any person aggrieved by the refusal of the Department to give its consent under paragraph (1) may, within 21 days of receiving notice thereof, appeal to the planning appeals commission by notice in writing under this Article.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(4) Paragraphs (2) and (3) of Article 84 apply to an appeal under this Article as they apply to an appeal under that Article.\r"]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Retaining walls", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "article-57"}], ["57."]}, "—(1) This Article applies to a retaining wall any part of which is within 6 metres of a road and which—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-57-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["is at any point of a height of one metre or more above the level of the ground at the boundary of the road nearest that point; or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-57-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["serves, or is intended to serve, as a support for earth or other material which supports a road."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) No retaining wall, being a wall which when erected will be a retaining wall to which this Article applies, shall be erected otherwise than in accordance with plans, sections and specifications approved by the Department.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) Any person who erects a retaining wall in contravention of paragraph (2) shall be guilty of an offence and liable on summary conviction to a fine not exceeding level 3 on the standard scale.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(4) Where—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-57-4-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a retaining wall to which this Article applies by virtue of paragraph (1)(a) is in such a condition as to constitute a danger to persons using the road; or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-57-4-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a retaining wall to which this Article applies by virtue of paragraph (1)(b) is in such a condition as to constitute a danger to the support and stability of a road,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["the Department may, by notice served on the owner or occupier of the land on which that wall is situated, require him to carry out such works as will obviate the danger.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(5) Any person aggrieved by the refusal of the Department to give its approval under paragraph (2) may, within 21 days of receiving notice thereof, appeal to the planning appeals commission by notice in writing under this Article.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(6) Paragraphs (2) and (3) of Article 84 apply to an appeal under this Article as they apply to an appeal under that Article.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(7) In this Article “retaining wall” means a wall, not forming part of a permanent building, which serves, or is intended to serve, as a support for earth or other material on one side only.\r"]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Notices under Articles 50 to 57 and appeals", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "article-58"}], ["58."]}, "—(1) This Article applies to notices served under any of Articles 50 to 57.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) A notice shall—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-58-2-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["describe the works to be carried out;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-58-2-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["require the person upon whom it is served to carry out those works within the specified period; and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-58-2-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["require that person within that period to do such other things necessary for or connected with the carrying out of those works as may be specified in the notice."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) Any person upon whom a notice is served who is aggrieved by any of its requirements may appeal within 21 days of its service to a court of summary jurisdiction.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(4) Subject to any order made on appeal, if a person upon whom a notice is served fails to comply with any of its requirements—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-58-4-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["he shall be guilty of an offence and liable on summary conviction to a fine not exceeding level 2 on the standard scale, and if after conviction the failure continues he shall be guilty of a further offence and liable on summary conviction to a fine not exceeding one-tenth of level 2 on the standard scale for each day on which the failure continues;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-58-4-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the Department may execute such works as are necessary to comply with the requirements of the notice and may recover from that person any expenses thereby reasonably incurred by it."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(5) Notice of the right of appeal under paragraph (3) shall be given in the notice.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(6) In this Article “specified period” means such period, being not less than 21 days from the service of the notice, as the Department specifies in the notice.\r"]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Removal of nuisances", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "article-59"}], ["59."]}, "—(1) Where any thing is placed on a road so as to constitute a nuisance, the Department may by notice require the person who placed it there to remove it immediately and if he fails to comply with the notice the Department may make a complaint to a court of summary jurisdiction for a removal and disposal order under this Article.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) Where the Department considers that any thing placed on a road without lawful authority constitutes a danger to persons using the road the Department may remove the thing and may make a complaint to a court of summary jurisdiction for a disposal order under this Article.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) A court of summary jurisdiction may, on a complaint made under this Article, make an order authorising the Department either to remove the thing in question and dispose of it or, as the case may be, to dispose of the thing in question.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(4) Where in accordance with an order under paragraph (3) any thing is disposed of by sale, the expenses of removal and sale shall be defrayed out of the proceeds thereof and the balance of the proceeds (if any) shall be given to the owner if known and if not shall be applied in the same manner as is provided for with respect to fines by section 20 of the Administration of Justice Act (Northern Ireland) 1954", {"a", [{"class", "LegCommentaryLink"}, {"href", "#commentary-c16867041"}, {"title", "View the commentary text for this item"}, {"id", "reference-c16867041"}], ["F31"]}, ".\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(5) Where in accordance with an order under paragraph (3) the Department disposes of any thing—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-59-5-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["by sale and the proceeds are not sufficient to defray the Department's expenses; or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-59-5-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["in some manner other than by sale,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["the Department may recover from the person who placed that thing on the road any expenses reasonably incurred by it in removing and disposing of the thing.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(6) For the purposes of this Article a thing may be treated as having been placed on a road notwithstanding that it is on wheels.\r"]}, {"div", [{"class", "LegAnnotations"}], [{"div", [{"class", "LegCommentaryItem"}, {"id", "commentary-c16867041"}], [{"p", [{"class", "LegCommentaryPara"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegCommentaryType"}], [{"a", [{"href", "#reference-c16867041"}, {"title", "Go back to reference for this commentary item"}], ["F31"]}]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegCommentaryText"}], [{"a", [{"class", "LegCitation"}, {"title", "Go to item of legislation"}, {"rel", "cite"}, {"href", "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/apni/1954/9"}], ["1954 c. 9 (N.I.)"]}]}]}]}]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Damage caused to road by excavations, etc. on adjoining land", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "article-60"}], ["60."]}, "  Where a road is damaged by or in consequence of any excavation or other works on land adjoining the road, the Department may make good the damage and recover from the owner or occupier of the land any expenses thereby reasonably incurred by it.\r"]}, {"div", [{"class", "LegClearPblock"}], []}, {"h3", [{"class", "LegPblock"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegPblockTitle"}], ["Miscellaneous powers of Department as to structures, works etc. in or under road", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitleFirst"}], ["Placing of structures in a road", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "article-61"}], ["61."]}, "—(1) Article 5 of the Social Need (Northern Ireland) Order 1986", {"a", [{"class", "LegCommentaryLink"}, {"href", "#commentary-c16867071"}, {"title", "View the commentary text for this item"}, {"id", "reference-c16867071"}], ["F32"]}, " shall be renumbered as paragraph (1) of that Article and after that paragraph there shall be added the following paragraphs—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText LegAmend"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAmendingText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAmendQuote"}], ["“"]}, "(2)"]}, " ", {"span", [{"class", "LegAmendingText"}], ["In the exercise of its powers under this Article the Department may carry out works involving the placing of any structure in a road maintained by it, but shall not so exercise those powers as—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container LegAmend"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3NoAmend"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAmendingText"}], ["(a)"]}]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3TextAmend"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAmendingText"}], ["to obstruct or prevent the passage of vehicles or of the public on foot along the road;"]}]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container LegAmend"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3NoAmend"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAmendingText"}], ["(b)"]}]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3TextAmend"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAmendingText"}], ["to obstruct or prevent normal access to premises adjoining the road;"]}]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container LegAmend"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3NoAmend"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAmendingText"}], ["(c)"]}]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3TextAmend"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAmendingText"}], ["to prevent any person from having access to any works of his under, in, on, over, along or across the road."]}]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText LegAmend"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAmendingText"}], ["(3)"]}, " ", {"span", [{"class", "LegAmendingText"}], ["The Department may sell, let or otherwise dispose of any structure placed by it in a road under this Article to any other person.", {"span", [{"class", "LegAmendQuote"}], ["”"]}]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) In Article 101 of the Planning Order after paragraph (2) there shall be inserted the following paragraph—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText LegAmend"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAmendingText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAmendQuote"}], ["“"]}, "(2A)"]}, " ", {"span", [{"class", "LegAmendingText"}], ["The Department may sell, let or otherwise dispose of any trading kiosk placed by it in a road under this Article to any other person.", {"span", [{"class", "LegAmendQuote"}], ["”"]}, " ."]}, "\r"]}, {"div", [{"class", "LegAnnotations"}], [{"div", [{"class", "LegCommentaryItem"}, {"id", "commentary-c16867071"}], [{"p", [{"class", "LegCommentaryPara"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegCommentaryType"}], [{"a", [{"href", "#reference-c16867071"}, {"title", "Go back to reference for this commentary item"}], ["F32"]}]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegCommentaryText"}], [{"a", [{"class", "LegCitation"}, {"title", "Go to item of legislation"}, {"rel", "cite"}, {"href", "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/nisi/1986"}], ["1986 NI 14"]}]}]}]}]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Trading kiosks", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "article-62"}], ["62."]}, "—(1) This Article applies to any trading kiosk which—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-62-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["having been placed in a road by the Department in the exercise of its powers under Article 5 of the Social Need (Northern Ireland) Order 1986 is sold by the Department to another person under paragraph (3) of that Article; or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-62-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["having been placed in a road by the Department or a district council in the exercise of its powers under Article 101 of the Planning Order, is sold by the Department or council to another person under paragraph (2A) or (5) of that Article."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) Where a trading kiosk to which this Article applies is present in a road, the owner of that kiosk shall, unless there is in force a licence under this Article authorising its presence in that road, be guilty of an offence and liable on summary conviction to a fine not exceeding level 3 on the standard scale.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) Where—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-62-3-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a person is convicted of an offence under paragraph (2); and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-62-3-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["he does not, within such period as the court may allow, remove the trading kiosk in question and make good any damage to the road,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["then the Department may itself—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "article-62-3-i"}], ["(i)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["remove that trading kiosk and dispose of it in such manner as the Department thinks fit; and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "article-62-3-ii"}], ["(ii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["make good any damage to the road."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(4) The Department may by a licence issued under this Article to the owner of a trading kiosk to which this Article applies authorise the presence of that trading kiosk in a road and in a position specified in the licence.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(5) The Department may—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-62-5-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["issue a licence under this Article to the owner of a trading kiosk and insert in the licence a provision prohibiting assignment of the licence; or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-62-5-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["issue such a licence to the owner of a trading kiosk and his successors in title, the licence, unless withdrawn or surrendered, to be transferred with the ownership of the trading kiosk;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["and references in this Article to the licensee are references to the person who is for the time being entitled to the benefit of a licence under this Article.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(6) A licence under this Article shall be issued subject to such conditions as the Department thinks fit.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(7) Without prejudice to the generality of paragraph (6), a licence under this Article may be issued subject to conditions—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-62-7-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["regulating the maintenance, repair and alteration of the trading kiosk to which the licence relates;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-62-7-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["requiring the licensee to give the Department not less than 6 weeks notice of his intention to cease using or abandon that trading kiosk."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(8) The Department may by notice served on the licensee withdraw a licence issued under this Article—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-62-8-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["on the expiration of such period as may be specified in the notice, being a period of not less than 7 days beginning with the date of service of the notice on the licensee, if—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "article-62-8-a-i"}], ["(i)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["any condition subject to which the licence was issued is contravened by the licensee; or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "article-62-8-a-ii"}], ["(ii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["the Department becomes aware that the licensee intends to cease using or abandon the trading kiosk;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-62-8-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["on the expiration of such period as may be so specified, being a period of not less than 3 months beginning with that date, if—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "article-62-8-b-i"}], ["(i)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["the Department considers the withdrawal of the licence is necessary for the purpose of the exercise of its functions under this Order; or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "article-62-8-b-ii"}], ["(ii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["in the case of a licence relating to a trading kiosk mentioned in paragraph (1)(b), an order under Article 100 of the Planning Order ceases to apply in relation to the road on which the kiosk is present."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(9) Unless withdrawn or surrendered by the licensee, a licence under this Article shall remain in force for such period as may be specified therein.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(10) Where a licence under this Article expires or is withdrawn or surrendered—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-62-10-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the Department may require the last licensee, within such period as the Department may specify, to remove the trading kiosk to which the licence relates and make good any damage to the road; and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-62-10-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["if the last licensee fails to comply with any such requirement the Department may itself—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "article-62-10-b-i"}], ["(i)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["remove that trading kiosk and dispose of it in such manner as the Department thinks fit; and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "article-62-10-b-ii"}], ["(ii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["make good any damage to the road."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(11) The licensee or (in the case of a licence which has expired or been withdrawn or surrendered) the last licensee shall indemnify the Department against any claim in respect of injury, damage or loss arising out of—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-62-11-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the presence in a road of the trading kiosk to which the licence relates; or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-62-11-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the carrying out by any person of any works required under paragraph (10),"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["other than a claim in respect of injury, damage or loss which is attributable to the negligence of the Department.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(12) In paragraphs (10) and (11) “the last licensee” means the person who, immediately before the expiration, withdrawal or surrender of the licence, was the licensee or, if that person has died, his personal representative.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(13) Where any trading kiosk is disposed of by sale under paragraph (3)(i) or (10)(b)(i) the expenses of removal and sale and of making good any damage to the road shall be defrayed out of the proceeds thereof and the balance of the proceeds (if any) shall be applied in the same manner as is provided for with respect to fines by section 20 of the Administration of Justice Act (Northern Ireland) 1954", {"a", [{"class", "LegCommentaryLink"}, {"href", "#commentary-c16867081"}, {"title", "View the commentary text for this item"}, {"id", "reference-c16867081"}], ["F33"]}, ".\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(14) Where the Department disposes of any trading kiosk under paragraph (3)(i) or (10)(b)(i)—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-62-14-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["by sale and the proceeds are not sufficient to defray the Department's expenses; or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-62-14-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["in some manner other than by sale,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["the Department may recover from the owner of the trading kiosk any expenses reasonably incurred by it in removing and disposing of the trading kiosk and making good any damage to the road.\r"]}, {"div", [{"class", "LegAnnotations"}], [{"div", [{"class", "LegCommentaryItem"}, {"id", "commentary-c16867081"}], [{"p", [{"class", "LegCommentaryPara"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegCommentaryType"}], [{"a", [{"href", "#reference-c16867081"}, {"title", "Go back to reference for this commentary item"}], ["F33"]}]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegCommentaryText"}], [{"a", [{"class", "LegCitation"}, {"title", "Go to item of legislation"}, {"rel", "cite"}, {"href", "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/apni/1954/9"}], ["1954 c. 9 (N.I.)"]}]}]}]}]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Cattle-grids", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "article-63"}], ["63."]}, "—(1) The Department may, if it is satisfied that it is expedient to do so, provide and maintain a cattle‐grid in a road or partly in a road and partly in adjoining land.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) Where the Department provides a cattle-grid under this Article it shall also provide facilities for the passage under proper control of animals and all other traffic unable to pass over the cattle-grid, being traffic entitled by law to use the road in which the grid is placed.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) A cattle-grid and any facilities provided by the Department under this Article shall, when completed, vest in and be maintainable by the Department.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(4) The Department may alter or improve a cattle-grid or facilities provided under this Article.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(5) The Department may enter into an agreement with any person for the making by him of a contribution (by a single payment or periodical payments) of such amount as may be specified in the agreement towards the expenses of the Department in providing and maintaining a cattle-grid under this Article.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(6) An agreement under paragraph (5) may include such incidental and consequential provisions as appear to the parties to be necessary, including provisions for the repayment of, if the cattle-grid is later removed, a specified proportion of a contribution towards the installation of the cattle-grid.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(7) The Department may, in determining whether or not to provide a cattle-grid, have regard to the extent to which persons who will receive special benefit from it are willing to enter into agreements under paragraph (5).\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(8) In this Article “cattle-grid” means a device intended to prevent the passage of animals, or animals of a particular description, but to allow the passage of all or some other traffic, and includes any fence or other works necessary for securing the efficient operation of the device.\r"]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Shelters, rails, barriers, etc.", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "article-64"}], ["64."]}, "—(1) The Department may erect or permit to be erected on any road—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-64-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["shelters for the protection from the weather of persons waiting to enter public service vehicles;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-64-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["rails or other barriers for the regulation of the priority of such persons;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-64-1-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [