ronmental statement or the details of the project were published before the coming into operation of the Roads (Environmental Impact Assessment) Regulations (Northern Ireland) 1999."]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegChangeDelimiter"}], ["]"]}, "\r"]}, {"a", [{"class", "LegAnchorID"}, {"id", "part-VI"}], []}, {"div", [{"class", "LegClearPart"}], []}, {"h2", [{"class", "LegPart"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegPartNo"}], ["PART VI", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegPartTitle"}], ["ABANDONMENT AND STOPPING-UP OF ROADS AND PRIVATE ACCESSES"]}]}, {"h3", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitleFirst"}], ["Abandonment and stopping-up of roads", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "article-68"}], ["68."]}, "—(1) The Department may by order provide for—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-68-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the abandonment of any road; or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-68-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the stopping-up of any road."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) On the coming into operation of an order for the abandonment of a road—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-68-2-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the road shall cease to be maintainable by the Department; and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-68-2-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["any public right of way over the road shall be extinguished."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) An order for the stopping-up of a road shall authorise the Department to carry out such works as it considers necessary to prevent or restrict to such extent as the Department thinks fit, access to the road by road traffic.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(4) No order shall be made under paragraph (1) in relation to a road unless—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-68-4-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the Department is of the opinion that the road is not necessary for road traffic or that another road is available which provides, or is capable, if improved, of providing, alternative facilities for road traffic; or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-68-4-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the order provides for the carrying out by the Department or any other person of such works as the Department considers necessary for the provision of alternative facilities for road traffic before the road is stopped-up or abandoned."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(5) An order made under paragraph (1) may—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-68-5-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["provide for the retention or removal of any cables, wires, mains, pipes or other apparatus placed along, across, over or under the stopped-up or abandoned road; and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-68-5-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["provide for the extinction, modification or preservation of any rights as to the use or maintenance of such cables, wires, mains, pipes or apparatus;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["and may contain such consequential, incidental and supplementary provisions as appear to the Department to be necessary or expedient for the purposes of the order.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(6) The Department may by order under this paragraph—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-68-6-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["revoke any order for the time being in operation under paragraph (1)(b); and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-68-6-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["authorise the removal of any works carried out in pursuance of such an order."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(7) Where all the owners and occupiers of land adjoining a road request the Department in writing to make an order under paragraph (1) in respect of the road, the Department may make such an order if (in addition to the condition mentioned in paragraph (4)(a) or (b) being fulfilled) it is satisfied that provision has been made, upon terms agreed by all the owners and occupiers and the Department, for the payment by the owners and occupiers of—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-68-7-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the costs of any works which by any provision of the order the Department or any other person is required to carry out;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-68-7-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the expenses of the Department in making the order; and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-68-7-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["compensation in respect of the extinction or modification by the order of any right of any person;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["and, accordingly, where an order is made under paragraph (1) at the request of all the owners and occupiers of land adjoining the road, they shall meet the costs and expenses and pay the compensation mentioned above.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(8) Where the Department makes an order under paragraph (1) otherwise than at the request of all the owners and occupiers of land adjoining the road, the Department shall—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-68-8-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["meet the costs of any works which by any provision of the order any person is required to carry out; and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-68-8-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["pay compensation in respect of the extinction or modification by the order of any right of any person."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(9) Any question of disputed compensation arising under this Article shall be referred to and determined by the Lands Tribunal.\r"]}, {"h3", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Stopping-up of private accesses", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "article-69"}], ["69."]}, "—(1) Where the Department considers that the use of a private means of access from a road to any land is likely to cause danger to, or to interfere unreasonably with, traffic on the road, the Department may make an order providing for—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-69-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the stopping-up of the access to the land;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-69-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the provision of a new means of access to the land."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) No order shall be made under paragraph (1)(a) unless the Department is satisfied that—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-69-2-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["access from the road to the land is not reasonably required; or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-69-2-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["another reasonably convenient means of access to the land is available or will be provided in pursuance of an order made under paragraph (1)(b)."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) The Department may agree with the occupiers of any land and any other person having an estate therein that any private means of access to the land from a road shall be stopped-up by it and, where it appears to the parties to be necessary, may provide a new means of access to the land.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(4) The Department may stop-up a means of access in any way that seems to it to be appropriate, but shall not do so in such a way as to obstruct any public right of way on foot.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(5) Schedule 5 shall have effect in relation to an order made under paragraph (1).\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(6) Any person, other than a person exercising a public right of way on foot, who uses a means of access which has been stopped-up under this Article shall be guilty of an offence and liable on summary conviction to a fine not exceeding level 3 on the standard scale.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(7) Article 19 (compensation where rights of access stopped-up or restricted) shall apply where access to any land has been stopped-up under this Article in the same manner at it applies where access to any land has been stopped-up under Article 18(1).\r"]}, {"a", [{"class", "LegAnchorID"}, {"id", "part-6A"}], []}, {"div", [{"class", "LegClearPart"}], []}, {"h2", [{"class", "LegPart"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegPartNo"}], [{"strong", [], [{"span", [{"class", "LegChangeDelimiter"}], ["["]}, {"a", [{"class", "LegCommentaryLink"}, {"href", "#commentary-key-df9554fbff6f05898122e8c1e2f42bd3"}, {"title", "View the commentary text for this item"}, {"id", "reference-key-df9554fbff6f05898122e8c1e2f42bd3"}], ["F112"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["PART 6A"]}]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegPartTitle"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["RESTRICTION OF RIGHTS OVER ROAD"]}]}]}, {"div", [{"class", "LegAnnotations"}], [{"div", [{"class", "LegCommentaryItem"}, {"id", "commentary-key-df9554fbff6f05898122e8c1e2f42bd3"}], [{"p", [{"class", "LegCommentaryPara"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegCommentaryType"}], [{"a", [{"href", "#reference-key-df9554fbff6f05898122e8c1e2f42bd3"}, {"title", "Go back to reference for this commentary item"}], ["F112"]}]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegCommentaryText"}], ["Pt. 6A inserted (1.4.2012) by ", {"a", [{"class", "LegCitation"}, {"title", "Clean Neighbourhoods and Environment Act (Northern Ireland) 2011"}, {"rel", "cite"}, {"href", "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/nia/2011/23"}], ["Clean Neighbourhoods and Environment Act (Northern Ireland) 2011 (c. 23)"]}, ", ", {"a", [{"class", "LegCitation"}, {"href", "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/nia/2011/23/section/1"}, {"title", "Go to Clean Neighbourhoods and Environment Act (Northern Ireland) 2011 ss. 1"}, {"rel", "cite"}], [{"strong", [], ["ss. 1"]}]}, ", ", {"a", [{"class", "LegCitation"}, {"href", "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/nia/2011/23/section/78"}, {"title", "Go to Clean Neighbourhoods and Environment Act (Northern Ireland) 2011 78"}, {"rel", "cite"}], ["78"]}, "; ", {"a", [{"class", "LegCitation"}, {"title", "The Clean Neighbourhoods and Environment (2011 Act) (Commencement, Savings and Transitional Provisions) Order (Northern Ireland) 2012"}, {"rel", "cite"}, {"href", "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/nisr/2012/13"}], ["S.R. 2012/13"]}, ", ", {"a", [{"class", "LegCitation"}, {"href", "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/nisr/2012/13/article/2/2"}, {"title", "Go to The Clean Neighbourhoods and Environment (2011 Act) (Commencement, Savings and Transitional Provisions) Order (Northern Ireland) 2012 art. 2(2)"}, {"rel", "cite"}], ["art. 2(2)"]}, ", ", {"a", [{"class", "LegCitation"}, {"href", "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/nisr/2012/13/schedule/2"}, {"title", "Go to The Clean Neighbourhoods and Environment (2011 Act) (Commencement, Savings and Transitional Provisions) Order (Northern Ireland) 2012 Sch. 2"}, {"rel", "cite"}], ["Sch. 2"]}]}]}]}]}, {"h3", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitleFirst"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["Gating orders"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "article-69A"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["69A"]}]}, "—", {"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["(1)"]}, " ", {"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["A district council may, with the approval of the Department, make an order under this Article in relation to any relevant road which is situated within its district."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["(2)"]}, " ", {"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["An order under this Article is to be known as a “gating order”."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["(3)"]}, " ", {"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["Before making a gating order in relation to a relevant road the district council must be satisfied that—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-69A-3-a"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["(a)"]}]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["premises adjoining or adjacent to the road are affected by crime or anti-social behaviour;"]}]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-69A-3-b"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["(b)"]}]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["the existence of the road is facilitating the persistent commission of criminal offences or anti-social behaviour; and"]}]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-69A-3-c"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["(c)"]}]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["it is in all the circumstances expedient to make the order for the purposes of reducing crime or anti-social behaviour."]}]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["(4)"]}, " ", {"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["The circumstances referred to in paragraph (3)(c) include—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-69A-4-a"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["(a)"]}]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["the likely effect of making the order on the occupiers of premises adjoining or adjacent to the road;"]}]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-69A-4-b"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["(b)"]}]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["the likely effect of making the order on other persons in the locality; and"]}]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-69A-4-c"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["(c)"]}]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["in a case where the road constitutes a through route, the availability of a reasonably convenient alternative route."]}]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["(5)"]}, " ", {"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["In this Article “"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegTerm"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["relevant road"]}]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["” means a road other than—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-69A-5-a"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["(a)"]}]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["a special road;"]}]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-69A-5-b"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["(b)"]}]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["a trunk road;"]}]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-69A-5-c"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["(c)"]}]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["a classified road;"]}]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-69A-5-d"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["(d)"]}]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["a road of such other description as the Department may by regulations prescribe."]}]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["(6)"]}, " ", {"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["For the purposes of this Part “"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegTerm"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["anti-social behaviour"]}]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["” means behaviour by a person which causes or is likely to cause harassment, alarm or distress to one or more other persons not of the same household as that person."]}, "\r"]}, {"h3", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["Effect of gating orders"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "article-69B"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["69B"]}]}, "—", {"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["(1)"]}, " ", {"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["A gating order restricts, to the extent specified in the order, the public right of way over the road to which it relates."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["(2)"]}, " ", {"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["A gating order may in particular—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-69B-2-a"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["(a)"]}]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["restrict the public right of way at all times, or in respect of such times, days or periods as may be specified in the order;"]}]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-69B-2-b"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["(b)"]}]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["exclude persons of a description specified in the order from the effect of the restriction."]}]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["(3)"]}, " ", {"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["A gating order may not be made so as to restrict the public right of way over a road for the occupiers of premises adjoining or adjacent to the road."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["(4)"]}, " ", {"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["A gating order may not be made so as to restrict the public right of way over a road which is the only or principal means of access to any dwelling."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["(5)"]}, " ", {"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["In relation to a road which is the only or principal means of access to any premises used for business or recreational purposes, a gating order may not be made so as to restrict the public right of way over the road during periods when those premises are normally used for those purposes."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["(6)"]}, " ", {"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["A gating order may authorise the installation, operation and maintenance of a barrier or barriers for the purpose of enforcing the restriction provided for in the order."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["(7)"]}, " ", {"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["A district council may install, operate and maintain any barrier authorised under paragraph (6)."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["(8)"]}, " ", {"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["A road in relation to which a gating order is made shall not cease to be regarded as a road by reason of the restriction of the public right of way under the order (or by reason of any barrier authorised under this Article)."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["(9)"]}, " ", {"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["In paragraph (4) “"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegTerm"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["dwelling"]}]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["” means any building or part of a building occupied, or intended to be occupied, as a separate dwelling."]}, "\r"]}, {"h3", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["Variation and revocation of gating orders"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "article-69C"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["69C"]}]}, "—", {"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["(1)"]}, " ", {"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["A district council may, with the approval of the Department, by order vary a gating order made by the council so as further to restrict any public right of way over the road to which the order relates, if the council is satisfied that in all the circumstances it is expedient to do so for the purpose of reducing crime or anti-social behaviour."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["(2)"]}, " ", {"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["A district council may by order vary a gating order made by it so as to reduce the restriction imposed by the order, if and to the extent that it is satisfied that the restriction is no longer expedient in all the circumstances for the purpose of reducing crime or anti-social behaviour."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["(3)"]}, " ", {"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["A district council may by order revoke a gating order made by it, if it is satisfied that the restriction imposed by the order is no longer expedient in all the circumstances for the purpose of reducing crime or anti-social behaviour."]}, "\r"]}, {"h3", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["Procedure for orders under this Part"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "article-69D"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["69D"]}]}, "—", {"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["(1)"]}, " ", {"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["Before making, varying or revoking a gating order a district council shall publish in the Belfast Gazette and once at least in each of two successive weeks in one or more newspapers circulating in the area in which the road to which the order relates is situated a notice—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-69D-1-a"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["(a)"]}]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["stating the general effect of the proposed order;"]}]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-69D-1-b"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["(b)"]}]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["specifying a place in that area where a copy of a draft of the order and of any relevant map or plan may be inspected by any person free of charge at all reasonable hours during a period of not less than 30 days from the date of the last publication of the notice; and"]}]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-69D-1-c"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["(c)"]}]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["stating that, within that period, any person may, by notice to the council, inform it of the grounds upon which he objects to the making of the order."]}]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["(2)"]}, " ", {"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["The district council shall, not later than the date on which the notice referred to in paragraph (1) is last published, serve a copy of the notice together with a copy of a draft of the order and of any relevant map or plan on—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-69D-2-a"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["(a)"]}]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["the occupiers of premises adjacent to or adjoining the road, and"]}]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-69D-2-b"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["(b)"]}]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["the owner of any cables, wires, mains, pipes or other apparatus placed along, across, over or under any road to which the order applies."]}]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["(3)"]}, " ", {"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["In the case of an order under Article 69A(1) or 69C(1), the district council shall, not later than the date on which the notice referred to in paragraph (1) is last published, cause a copy of that notice to be displayed in a prominent position on the road to which the order relates."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["(4)"]}, " ", {"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["Where, before the expiration of the period referred to in paragraph (1)(b), the district council proposes to modify the terms of the draft of an order, the council shall give and publish, in such manner as appears to it to be appropriate, such additional notices as the council considers appropriate for informing all persons likely to be adversely affected by the modification."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["(5)"]}, " ", {"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["If, before the expiration of the period referred to in paragraph (1)(b), the district council receives an objection from any person on whom a copy of the notice is required to be served under paragraph (2) or from any other person appearing to it to be affected, it shall, subject to paragraph (6), cause a local inquiry to be held unless the objection is withdrawn."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["(6)"]}, " ", {"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["Unless the objection is made by a person on whom a no