egP4No"}, {"id", "article-73-3-i"}], ["(i)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["remove that apparatus or carry out such other works as are necessary to obviate the danger; and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "article-73-3-ii"}], ["(ii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["recover from that person any expenses thereby reasonably incurred by it."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(4) Any person convicted of an offence under paragraph (1) shall, within such period as the court may allow, remove any apparatus fixed or placed in contravention of that paragraph and if he fails to do so he shall be guilty of a further offence and be liable on summary conviction to a fine not exceeding one-tenth of level 2 on the standard scale for each day upon which that failure continues.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(5) Where a person who has been convicted of an offence under paragraph (1) becomes liable to prosecution for an offence under paragraph (4), the Department may itself do anything which he has failed to do and recover from that person any expenses thereby reasonably incurred by it.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(6) A consent under paragraph (2)(a) may be given by the Department where it is satisfied that the safety or convenience of traffic using the road, or which may be expected to use the road, will not thereby be prejudiced.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(7) A consent under paragraph (2)(a) shall be given subject to such conditions as seem to the Department to be adequate for securing the safety and convenience of traffic.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(8) Without prejudice to the generality of paragraph (7), a consent under paragraph (2)(a) may be given subject to conditions—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-73-8-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["requiring the person to whom the consent is given to insure against such risks in connection with the fixing or placing of the apparatus to which the consent relates and its presence over, along or across a road as the Department may specify;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-73-8-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["requiring the person to whom the consent is given to produce to the Department such certificates as the Department may require as to the safety of any apparatus to which the consent relates;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-73-8-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["requiring the apparatus to be fixed or placed not earlier than such date as is specified in the consent and to be removed not later than such other date as is so specified."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(9) The person to whom a consent under paragraph (2)(a) is given shall indemnify the Department against any claim in respect of injury, damage or loss arising out of the fixing, placing or presence over, along or across a road of apparatus to which the consent relates, other than a claim in respect of injury, damage or loss which is attributable to the negligence of the Department.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(10) Any person who—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-73-10-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["fixes or places any apparatus in pursuance of a consent given under paragraph (2)(a); and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-73-10-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["fails to comply with any condition subject to which that consent was given,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["shall be guilty of an offence and liable on summary conviction to a fine not exceeding level 2 on the standard scale.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(11) Where it appears to the Department that a person has contravened paragraph (10), then (whether or not proceedings are instituted for an offence under that paragraph) the Department may—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-73-11-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["revoke the consent given to that person under paragraph (2)(a);"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-73-11-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["remove any apparatus fixed or placed in pursuance of the consent; and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-73-11-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["recover from that person any expenses thereby reasonably incurred by it."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(12) Where any apparatus—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-73-12-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["has been removed by the Department under paragraph (3), (5) or (11); and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-73-12-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["has not been recovered by its owner within 21 days from the day on which it was removed,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["the Department may dispose of it in such manner as the Department thinks fit.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(13) Where any apparatus is disposed of by sale under paragraph (12) the expenses of removal and sale shall be defrayed out of the proceeds thereof and the balance of the proceeds (if any) shall be given to the owner if known and if not shall be applied in the same manner as is provided for with respect to fines by section 20 of the Administration of Justice Act (Northern Ireland) 1954", {"a", [{"class", "LegCommentaryLink"}, {"href", "#commentary-c16867351"}, {"title", "View the commentary text for this item"}, {"id", "reference-c16867351"}], ["F122"]}, ".\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(14) Where the Department disposes of any apparatus under paragraph (12)—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-73-14-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["by sale and the proceeds are not sufficient to defray the Department's expenses; or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-73-14-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["in some manner other than by sale,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["the Department may recover from the person who fixed or placed the apparatus over, along or across the road any expenses reasonably incurred by it in removing and disposing of the apparatus.\r"]}, {"div", [{"class", "LegAnnotations"}], [{"div", [{"class", "LegCommentaryItem"}, {"id", "commentary-c16867261"}], [{"p", [{"class", "LegCommentaryPara"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegCommentaryType"}], [{"a", [{"href", "#reference-c16867261"}, {"title", "Go back to reference for this commentary item"}], ["F120"]}]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegCommentaryText"}], [{"a", [{"class", "LegCitation"}, {"title", "Go to item of legislation"}, {"rel", "cite"}, {"href", "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/nisi/1995"}], ["1995 NI 19"]}]}]}]}, {"div", [{"class", "LegCommentaryItem"}, {"id", "commentary-c16867281"}], [{"p", [{"class", "LegCommentaryPara"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegCommentaryType"}], [{"a", [{"href", "#reference-c16867281"}, {"title", "Go back to reference for this commentary item"}], ["F121"]}]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegCommentaryText"}], [{"a", [{"class", "LegCitation"}, {"title", "Go to item of legislation"}, {"rel", "cite"}, {"href", "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ukpga/2003/21"}], ["2003 c. 21"]}]}]}]}, {"div", [{"class", "LegCommentaryItem"}, {"id", "commentary-c16867351"}], [{"p", [{"class", "LegCommentaryPara"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegCommentaryType"}], [{"a", [{"href", "#reference-c16867351"}, {"title", "Go back to reference for this commentary item"}], ["F122"]}]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegCommentaryText"}], [{"a", [{"class", "LegCitation"}, {"title", "Go to item of legislation"}, {"rel", "cite"}, {"href", "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/apni/1954/9"}], ["1954 c. 9 (N.I.)"]}]}]}]}]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Festive lighting on roads", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "article-74"}], ["74."]}, "—(1) The Department may issue to any person a licence authorising that person to place festive lighting over, along or across any road specified in the licence for such period as is so specified.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) A licence under paragraph (1) may be issued subject to such conditions as the Department thinks fit, and in particular conditions—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-74-2-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["regulating the installation of the festive lighting and the use for that purpose of any system of illumination installed under Article 44;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-74-2-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["requiring the payment by the licensee of charges in respect of electricity consumed by the festive lighting;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-74-2-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["requiring the licensee to indemnify the Department against any liability to any other person for injury, loss or damage arising from the placing of the festive lighting over, along or across a road."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) Any person who—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-74-3-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["places festive lighting over, along or across a road otherwise than in accordance with a licence granted under paragraph (1); or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-74-3-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["fails to comply with any condition subject to which such a licence is granted to him,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["shall be guilty of an offence and liable on summary conviction to a fine not exceeding level 3 on the standard scale.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(4) In this Article “festive lighting” means lighting which is installed for a temporary period in connection with the celebration of a festive occasion, season or event.\r"]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Restriction on construction of buildings over road", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "article-75"}], ["75."]}, "—(1) No person shall—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-75-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["except in the exercise of statutory powers, construct a building over any part of a road (whether it is intended to span the road or not), or alter a building so constructed, without a licence issued under this Article by the Department, or otherwise than in accordance with the conditions of a licence so issued;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-75-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["use a building so constructed or altered in pursuance of a licence so issued otherwise than in accordance with the conditions thereof;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["and any person who contravenes any provision of this paragraph is guilty of an offence and liable on summary conviction to a fine not exceeding level 3 on the standard scale; and if the contravention is continued after conviction, he shall be guilty of a further offence and liable to a fine not exceeding one-tenth of level 3 on the standard scale for each day on which the contravention is so continued.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) A licence under this Article may be issued subject to such conditions, including conditions with respect to the construction (including the headway over the road), maintenance, lighting and use of the building, as the Department thinks fit; and, any such condition is binding on the successor in title to every owner, and every lessee and occupier, of the building.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) Where a licence under this Article makes provision for the execution of any works or the provision of any facilities which in the opinion of the Department require to be executed or provided by it in connection with the building or its construction or alteration, the Department may execute those works or, as the case may be, provide those facilities and may recover the expenses reasonably incurred by it in so doing from the licensee or from the owner of the building.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(4) No appeal lies under Article 84—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-75-4-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["if the land on which the road in question is situated is owned by the Department, or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-75-4-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["against any condition which the Department declares to be necessary for the purpose of securing the safety of persons using the road or of preventing interference with traffic thereon."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(5) Where a person has constructed or altered a building, for the construction, or, as the case may be, alteration, of which a licence is required by this Article, without such a licence or otherwise than in accordance with the conditions of the licence, the Department may by notice served on the licensee or the owner of the building require him to remove the building or make alterations therein.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(6) Where there has been a failure to comply with any conditions of a licence under this Article with respect to the maintenance or use of a building, the Department may by notice served on the licensee or the owner of the building require him to execute such works or take such steps as are necessary to secure compliance with those conditions.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(7) Article 58 applies to a notice served under this Article as it applies to a notice served as mentioned in paragraph (1) of that Article.\r"]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Restriction on construction of bridges over road", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "article-76"}], ["76."]}, "—(1) The Department may issue to the owner or occupier of any land adjoining a road a licence to construct and use a bridge over the road.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) Subject to paragraph (3), a licence under this Article may be issued subject to such conditions as the Department thinks fit.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) It shall be a condition of every licence under this Article that the person to whom it is granted is, at his own expense, to remove the bridge or alter it in such manner as the Department may require, if at any time the Department considers the removal or alteration necessary or desirable in connection with the carrying out of improvements to the road; and the decision of the Department that the removal or alteration is necessary or desirable in that connection shall be final, and the condition shall be enforceable by the Department against the owner for the time being of the land.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(4) No appeal lies under Article 84 against—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-76-4-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["any condition mentioned in paragraph (3); or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-76-4-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["any condition which the Department declares to be necessary for the purpose of securing the safety of persons using the road or of preventing interference with traffic thereon."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(5) Any person who, except in the exercise of statutory powers—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-76-5-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["constructs a bridge over a road without a licence under this Article, or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-76-5-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["constructs or uses a bridge otherwise than in accordance with the conditions of such a licence, or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-76-5-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["fails to remove or alter a bridge when required to do so in accordance with any condition of the licence,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["shall be guilty of an offence and liable to a fine not exceeding level 3 on the standard scale, and if the offence is continued after conviction he shall be guilty of a further offence and liable to a fine not exceeding one-tenth of level 3 on the standard scale for each day on which the offence is so continued.\r"]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Restriction on construction of cellars, etc. under road", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "article-77"}], ["77."]}, "—(1) Any person who without the consent of the Department constructs any vault, arch, cellar or part of a building under a road shall be guilty of an offence and liable on summary conviction to a fine not exceeding level 3 on the standard scale.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) The consent of the Department—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-77-2-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["shall be given subject to the condition that any vault, arch or cellar constructed in pursuance of the consent and any gratings, lights and other fixtures in the surface of the road that are associated with it are to be kept in such good condition and repair by the person to whom the consent is given as not to constitute a danger or a nuisance to road users;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-77-2-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["may be given subject to such other conditions as the Department thinks fit."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) Where a person—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-77-3-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["constructs any vault, arch, cellar or part of a building in pursuance of a consent under this Article; and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-77-3-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["fails to comply with any condition subject to which that consent was given,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["he shall be guilty of an offence and liable on summary conviction to a fine not exceeding level 3 on the standard scale.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(4) Where it appears to the Department that a person has contravened paragraph (1) or (3) then (whether or not proceedings are instituted for an offence under that paragraph) the Department may serve on that person a notice requiring him to remove or alter the vault, arch, cellar or part of a building in question.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(5) Article 58 applies to a notice served under paragraph (4) as it applies to a notice served as mentioned in paragraph (1) of that Article.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(6) The person to whom a consent is given under this Article shall indemnify the Department against any claim in respect of injury, damage or loss arising out of—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-77-6-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the presence under a road of any vault, arch, cellar or part of a building to which the consent relates; or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-77-6-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the carrying out by any person of any works for the construction of any vault, arch, cellar or part of a building in pursuance of the consent."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegChangeDelimiter"}], ["["]}, {"a", [{"class", "LegCommentaryLink"}, {"href", "#commentary-c16867361"}, {"title", "View the commentary text for this item"}, {"id", "reference-c16867361"}], ["F123"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["(7)"]}, " ", {"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], ["This Article does not apply to street works within the meaning of the Street Works Order."]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegChangeDelimiter"}], ["]"]}, "\r"]}, {"div", [{"class", "LegAnnotations"}], [{"div", [{"class", "LegCommentaryItem"}, {"id", "commentar