0344821"}, {"title", "View the commentary text for this item"}, {"id", "reference-c20344821"}], ["F128"]}, ". . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .\r"]}, {"div", [{"class", "LegAnnotations"}], [{"div", [{"class", "LegCommentaryItem"}, {"id", "commentary-c20344821"}], [{"p", [{"class", "LegCommentaryPara"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegCommentaryType"}], [{"a", [{"href", "#reference-c20344821"}, {"title", "Go back to reference for this commentary item"}], ["F128"]}]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegCommentaryText"}], ["Art. 79 repealed (9.1.2006) by ", {"a", [{"class", "LegCitation"}, {"title", "Street Works (Northern Ireland) Order 1995"}, {"rel", "cite"}, {"href", "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/nisi/1995/3120"}], ["Street Works (Northern Ireland) Order 1995 (S.I. 1995/3120 (N.I. 19))"]}, ", ", {"a", [{"class", "LegCitation"}, {"href", "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/nisi/1995/3120/article/1/2"}, {"title", "Go to Street Works (Northern Ireland) Order 1995 arts. 1(2)"}, {"rel", "cite"}], ["arts. 1(2)"]}, ", ", {"a", [{"class", "LegCitation"}, {"href", "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/nisi/1995/3120/article/60/2"}, {"title", "Go to Street Works (Northern Ireland) Order 1995 60(2)"}, {"rel", "cite"}], ["60(2)"]}, ", ", {"a", [{"class", "LegCitation"}, {"href", "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/nisi/1995/3120/schedule/4"}, {"title", "Go to Street Works (Northern Ireland) Order 1995 Sch. 4"}, {"rel", "cite"}], [{"strong", [], ["Sch. 4"]}]}, "; ", {"a", [{"class", "LegCitation"}, {"title", "Go to item of legislation"}, {"rel", "cite"}, {"href", "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/nisr/2005/566"}], ["S.R. 2005/566"]}, ", ", {"a", [{"class", "LegCitation"}, {"href", "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/nisr/2005/566/article/2"}, {"title", "Go to S.R. 2005/566 art. 2"}, {"rel", "cite"}], [{"strong", [], ["art. 2"]}]}]}]}]}]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Construction of permitted means of access to a road", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "article-80"}], ["80."]}, "—(1) Subject to paragraphs (2) and (3), any person who, without the consent of the Department, constructs any permitted means of access to—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-80-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a trunk road or classified road from agricultural land; or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-80-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["any other road,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["shall be guilty of an offence and liable on summary conviction to a fine not exceeding level 3 on the standard scale.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) Paragraph (1) does not apply—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-80-2-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["if planning permission has been granted in respect of the construction of the means of access; or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-80-2-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["to anything done for the sole purpose of repairing any lawful work or of restoring it to substantially the form in which it was at any time within the preceding 3 years."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) Sub-paragraph (b) of paragraph (1) does not apply if the means of access is constructed in compliance with such requirements as to the siting and layout of means of access to roads of the kind mentioned in that sub-paragraph as may be prescribed by regulations made by the Department.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(4) Where—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-80-4-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a person has constructed a means of access in contravention of paragraph (1); and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-80-4-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the Department considers that the existence or use of the means of access constitutes a danger to persons using the road,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["then, (whether or not proceedings are instituted for an offence under that paragraph) the Department may—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "article-80-4-i"}], ["(i)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["stop-up the means of access and carry out such other works as are necessary to obviate the danger, and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "article-80-4-ii"}], ["(ii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["recover from that person any expenses thereby reasonably incurred by it."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(5) Where a person has constructed a means of access in contravention of paragraph (1), the Department may serve on that person a notice requiring that the means of access be stopped-up; and where, within 21 days from the date on which a notice is served on any person under this paragraph, a means of access is stopped-up in compliance with the notice, that person shall not be liable to prosecution for an offence under paragraph (1) in respect of that means of access.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(6) Any person, other than a person exercising a public right of way on foot, who uses a means of access stopped-up under paragraph (4) or in compliance with a notice under paragraph (5) shall be guilty of an offence and liable on summary conviction to a fine not exceeding level 3 on the standard scale.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(7) Where—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-80-7-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a person is convicted of an offence under paragraph (1); and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-80-7-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["he does not, within such period as the court may allow, remove any means of access constructed in contravention of that paragraph and make good any damage to the road,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["then the Department may itself—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "article-80-7-i"}], ["(i)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["remove that means of access and make good any damage to the road; and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "article-80-7-ii"}], ["(ii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["recover from that person any expenses thereby reasonably incurred by it."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(8) A consent under paragraph (1) may be given by the Department where it is satisfied that the safety or convenience of traffic using the road, or which may be expected to use the road, will not thereby be prejudiced.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(9) A consent under paragraph (1) shall be given subject to such conditions as seem to the Department to be adequate for securing—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-80-9-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the proper completion of the means of access and reinstatement of the road; and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-80-9-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the safety and convenience of traffic."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(10) Without prejudice to the generality of paragraph (9), a consent under paragraph (1) may be given subject to conditions—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-80-10-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["designed to ensure—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "article-80-10-a-i"}], ["(i)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["safe access to the road for traffic likely to use the road as a result of the construction of the means of access; and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "article-80-10-a-ii"}], ["(ii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["the provision of adequate accommodation adjoining the road for vehicles which, by waiting to load or unload or otherwise using the road for any purpose relating to the construction of the means of access, might reasonably be expected to obstruct the traffic on the road;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-80-10-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["requiring the deposit by the person to whom the consent is given of a sum of money as security for the