le.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) Where—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-81-2-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a person has carried out any works in contravention of paragraph (1); and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-81-2-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the Department considers that the works constitute a danger to persons using the road,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["then (whether or not proceedings are instituted for an offence under that paragraph), the Department may—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "article-81-2-i"}], ["(i)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["carry out such works as are necessary to obviate the danger; and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "article-81-2-ii"}], ["(ii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["recover from that person any expenses thereby reasonably incurred by it."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) Where—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-81-3-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a person is convicted of an offence under paragraph (1); and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-81-3-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["he does not, within such period as the court may allow, remove any works carried out in contravention of that paragraph and make good any damage to the road,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["then the Department may itself—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "article-81-3-i"}], ["(i)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["remove those works and make good any damage to the road; and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "article-81-3-ii"}], ["(ii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["recover from that person any expenses thereby reasonably incurred by it."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(4) A consent under paragraph (1) may be given by the Department where it is satisfied that the safety or convenience of traffic using the road, or which may be expected to use the road, will not thereby be prejudiced.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(5) A consent under paragraph (1) shall be given subject to such conditions as seem to the Department to be adequate for securing—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-81-5-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the proper completion of the works and reinstatement of the road; and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-81-5-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the safety and convenience of traffic."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(6) Without prejudice to the generality of paragraph (5), a consent under paragraph (1) may be given subject to conditions—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-81-6-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["requiring the deposit by the person to whom the consent is given of a sum of money as security for the completion of the works to which the consent relates;"]}, "\r"]}, 