y carry out—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-116-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["on land acquired by it under this Part;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-116-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["on any other land belonging to it;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-116-1-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["on any road,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["works for mitigating any adverse effect which the construction, improvement, alteration, existence or use of a road has, or will have, on the surroundings of the road.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) Without prejudice to the generality of paragraph (1), the works that may be carried out under that paragraph include the planting of trees, shrubs or plants of any other description and the laying out of any area as grassland.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) Notwithstanding anything in the Land Clauses Consolidation Act 1845", {"a", [{"class", "LegCommentaryLink"}, {"href", "#commentary-c16867941"}, {"title", "View the commentary text for this item"}, {"id", "reference-c16867941"}], ["F161"]}, ", the Department may develop or redevelop any land acquired by it under this Part, or any other land belonging to it, for the purpose of improving the surroundings of a road in any manner which it thinks desirable by reason of its construction, improvement, alteration, existence or use.\r"]}, {"div", [{"class", "LegAnnotations"}], [{"div", [{"class", "LegCommentaryItem"}, {"id", "commentary-c16867941"}], [{"p", [{"class", "LegCommentaryPara"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegCommentaryType"}], [{"a", [{"href", "#reference-c16867941"}, {"title", "Go back to reference for this commentary item"}], ["F161"]}]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegCommentaryText"}], [{"a", [{"class", "LegCitation"}, {"title", "Go to item of legislation"}, {"rel", "cite"}, {"href", "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ukpga/1845/18"}], ["1845 c. 18"]}]}]}]}]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Agreements as to use of land near roads", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "article-117"}], ["117."]}, "—(1) For the purpose of mitigating any adverse effect which the construction, improvement, alteration, existence or use of a road has or will have on the surroundings of the road, the Department may enter into an agreement with any person interested in land adjoining or in the vicinity of the road for restricting or regulating the use of the land either permanently or during such period as may be specified in the agreement.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) An agreement under this Article may, in particular, make provision for the planting and maintenance of trees, shrubs or plants of any other description on the land and for restricting the lopping or removal of trees, shrubs or other plants on the land.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) An agreement under this Article may contain such incidental and consequential provisions (including provisions of a financial character) as appear to the Department to be necessary or expedient for the purposes of the agreement.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(4) Subject to Part X of the Land Registration Act (Northern Ireland) 1970", {"a", [{"class", "LegCommentaryLink"}, {"href", "#commentary-c16867951"}, {"title", "View the commentary text for this item"}, {"id", "reference-c16867951"}], ["F162"]}, ", the provisions of any 