[{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-122-5-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["direct that any means of access or other facility afforded by the works to which the agreement relates shall not be used until that amount has been paid;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-122-5-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["recover that amount from any person having an estate in any land for the benefit of which any such means of access or other facility is afforded; and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-122-5-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["declare that amount to be a charge on any such land (identifying it) and on all estates therein."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(6) If it appears to the Department that a direction under paragraph (5)(a) is not being complied with, the Department may execute such works as are necessary to stop up the means of access or deny the facility, as the case may be, and may for that purpose enter any land.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(7) Where the Department recovers an amount from a person by virtue of paragraph (5)(b), he may in turn recover from any other person having an estate in land for the benefit of which the means of access or other facility was afforded such contribution as may be found by the court to be just and equitable.\r"]}, {"div", [{"class", "LegBlockText"}], [{"p", [{"class", "LegLevel3"}], ["This does not affect the right of any of those persons to recover from the person liable under the agreement the amount which they are made to pay.\r"]}]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Recovery of certain expenses by Department", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "article-123"}], ["123."]}, "  Where any provision of this Order enables the Department to recover expenses which it has incurred in exercising any function under this Order—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-123-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["those expenses shall include the relevant administrative expenses of the Department, including an appropriate sum in respect of general staff costs and overheads; and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-123-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the Department may recover those expenses summarily or in any court of competent jurisdiction as a civil debt due to it."]}, "\r"]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Repayment of charges, rates and tolls", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "article-124"}], ["124."]}, "—(1) A provision in this Order conferring power to make provision for payment of a charge shall be treated as also conferring power to make provision about repayment of sums paid, or purported to be paid, in pursuance of provision made in exercise of that power.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) Without prejudice to the generality of the power conferred by paragraph (1), the provision which may be made by virtue of that paragraph includes provision—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-124-2-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["that repayment shall be made only if a specified person is satisfied that specified conditions are met or in other specified circumstances;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-124-2-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["that repayment shall be made in part only;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-124-2-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["that, in the case of partial repayment, the amount shall be a specified sum or determined in a specified manner; and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-124-2-d"}], ["(d)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["for repayment of different amounts in different circumstances."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) In this Article—\r"]}, {"ul", [{"class", "LegTabbed LegUnorderedList"}], [{"li", [], [{"p", [{"class", "LegListTextStandard LegLevel3"}], ["“charge” includes rates and toll;\r"]}]}, {"li", [], [{"p", [{"class", "LegListTextStandard LegLevel3"}], ["“specified” means specified in the instrument exercising the power.\r"]}]}]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Power to pay expenses of persons moving temporarily during works for construction or improvement of road", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "article-125"}], ["125."]}, "—(1) This Article has effect where—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-125-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["works are carried out by the Department for the construction or improvement of a road; and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "article-125-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the carrying out of those works affects the enjoyment of a dwelling adjacent to the site on which they are being carried out to such an extent that continued occupation of the dwelling is not reasonably practicable."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) Subject to paragraph (3), the Department may pay any reasonable expenses incurred by the occupier of the dwelling in providing suitable alternative residential accommodation for himself and members of his household for the whole or any part of the period during which the works are being carried out.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) No payment shall be made to any person under this Article in respect of any expenses except in pursuance of an agreement made between that person and the Department before the expenses are incurred; and no payment shall be so made except in respect of the amount by which the expenses exceed those which that person would have incurred if the dwelling had continued to be occupied.\r"]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Loans to certain undertakings affected by acquisition of land", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "article-126"}], ["126."]}, "—(1) For the purpose of enabling a person carrying on a relevant undertaking to purchase or take on lease any land or to erect any buildings, 