itle", "Go to Transfer of Undertakings (Protection of Employment) Regulations 2006 reg. 21(1)"}, {"rel", "cite"}], ["reg. 21(1)"]}, ")"]}]}]}]}, {"a", [{"class", "LegAnchorID"}, {"id", "schedule-3"}], []}, {"div", [{"class", "LegClearSchedule"}], []}, {"p", [{"class", "LegArticleRef"}], ["Article 28(3)."]}, {"h2", [{"class", "LegSchedule"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegScheduleNo LegHeadingRef"}], ["SCHEDULE 3", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegTitleBlockTitle"}], ["PROCEDURE IN CONNECTION WITH TOLL ORDERS"]}]}, {"a", [{"class", "LegAnchorID"}, {"id", "schedule-3-part-1"}], []}, {"div", [{"class", "LegClearPartFirst"}], []}, {"h3", [{"class", "LegPartFirst"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegPartTitle"}], ["Publicity for proposals", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText LegExtentContainer"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-1"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-1"}], ["1."]}, "—(1) Where the Department proposes to make a toll order, it shall prepare a draft of the order and shall publish in at least one local newspaper circulating in the area in which the proposed special road is to be situated a notice—", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-1-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["stating the general effect of the proposed order;"]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-1-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["specifying a place in that area where a copy of the draft order may be inspected by any person free of charge at all reasonable hours during a period specified in the notice, being a period of not less than 30 days from the date of the publication of the notice; and"]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-1-1-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["stating that, within that period, any person may by notice to the Department object to the making of the order."]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-1"}], ["(2) Where the special road to which the toll order relates is to be subject to a concession, the Department shall make available for inspection with the copy of the draft order a statement containing such information as the Department considers appropriate with respect to the concessionaire and the concession agreement."]}, {"div", [{"class", "LegBlockText"}], [{"p", [{"class", "LegLevel3"}], ["The notice under sub-paragraph (1) shall indicate that such a statement will be so available for inspection.\r"]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-1"}], ["(3) Before or after the end of the period specified in the notice in pursuance of sub-paragraph (1), the Department may by a further notice published in the same manner substitute a longer period for that specified in the first notice."]}, {"a", [{"class", "LegAnchorID"}, {"id", "schedule-3-part-2"}], []}, {"div", [{"class", "LegClearPart"}], []}, {"h3", [{"class", "LegPart"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegPartTitle"}], ["Making of objections", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText LegExtentContainer"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-2"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-2"}], ["2."]}, "—(1) A person who objects to the making of a toll order shall include in the notice of objection a statement of the grounds of objection.", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-2"}], ["(2) If that is not done, the Department may disregard the objection."]}, {"a", [{"class", "LegAnchorID"}, {"id", "schedule-3-part-3"}], []}, {"div", [{"class", "LegClearPart"}], []}, {"h3", [{"class", "LegPart"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegPartTitle"}], ["Local inquiry", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText LegExtentContainer"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-3"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-3"}], ["3."]}, "—(1) If an objection is received by the Department within the period specified for making objections, and is not withdrawn, then the Department shall cause a local inquiry to be held unless it is satisfied that in the circumstances of the case it is unnecessary.", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-3"}], ["(2) The period specified for making objections means the period specified in the notice under paragraph 1(1) or any longer period substituted by a further notice under paragraph 1(3)."]}, {"a", [{"class", "LegAnchorID"}, {"id", "schedule-3-part-4"}], []}, {"div", [{"class", "LegClearPart"}], []}, {"h3", [{"class", "LegPart"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegPartTitle"}], ["Making or confirmation of order", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText LegExtentContainer"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-4"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-4"}], ["4."]}, "—(1) The Department, after considering—", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-4-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["any objections which are not withdrawn; and"]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-4-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["where a local inquiry is held, the report of the person who held the inquiry,"]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["may make the order either without modification or subject to such modifications as it thinks fit.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-4"}], ["(2) Where it proposes to make the order subject to modifications which will in its opinion make a substantial change in the order, the Department shall—"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-4-2-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["notify any person who appears to it to be likely to be affected by the proposed modifications;"]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-4-2-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["give that person an opportunity of making representations with respect to the modifications within such reasonable period as it may specify; and"]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-4-2-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["consider any representations made to it within that period with respect to the proposed modifications."]}]}, {"a", [{"class", "LegAnchorID"}, {"id", "schedule-3-part-5"}], []}, {"div", [{"class", "LegClearPart"}], []}, {"h3", [{"class", "LegPart"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegPartTitle"}], ["Assembly procedure", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText LegExtentContainer"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5"}], ["5."]}, "—(1) Except as provided by sub-paragraph (2), a toll order shall be subject to negative resolution.", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5"}], ["(2) A toll order shall be subject to affirmative resolution where—"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-2-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the proposed special road to which the order relates includes in its proposed route any existing road; and"]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-2-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the toll order authorises the charging of tolls for the use of that existing road or any part of it,"]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["unless the Department is satisfied as regards all classes of traffic entitled to use the existing road that another reasonably convenient route free of toll is available, or will be provided before the date on which the toll order will come into operation, and certifies accordingly.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5"}], ["(3) Where the Department proposes to give such a certificate, it shall—"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-3-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["give public notice of its intention to do so;"]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-3-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["afford an opportunity to all persons interested to make representations and objections; and"]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-3-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["cause a public local inquiry to be held if it appears to it to be expedient to do so, having regard to representations or objections made,"]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["and before deciding whether to give the certificate the Department shall consider any representations and objections made and, if an inquiry has been held, the report of the person who held the inquiry.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5"}], ["(4) As soon as may be after giving a certificate, the Department shall publish in the Belfast Gazette, and in such other manner as it thinks best for informing persons affected, a notice stating that the certificate has been given."]}, {"a", [{"class", "LegAnchorID"}, {"id", "schedule-4"}], []}, {"div", [{"class", "LegClearSchedule"}], []}, {"p", [{"class", "LegArticleRef"}], ["Article 49."]}, {"h2", [{"class", "LegSchedule"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegScheduleNo LegHeadingRef"}], ["SCHEDULE 4", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegTitleBlockTitle"}], ["PREVENTION OF OBSTRUCTION TO VIEW, ", {"span", [{"xml:lang", "la"}], ["ETC."]}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText LegExtentContainer"}, {"id", "schedule-4-paragraph-1"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "schedule-4-paragraph-1"}], ["1."]}, "—(1) Notice under Article 49 may be served—", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-4-paragraph-1-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["upon the owner or occupier of the land directing him—"]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "schedule-4-paragraph-1-1-a-i"}], ["(i)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["to remove any building or structure whether permanent or temporary, the removal of which is in the opinion of the Department expedient for the prevention of any such danger as is mentioned in that Article;"]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "schedule-4-paragraph-1-1-a-ii"}], ["(ii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["to provide or improve any means of access to any building or structure;"]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "schedule-4-paragraph-1-1-a-iii"}], ["(iii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["to provide or improve any accommodation for vehicles standing or waiting for any purpose connected with the user of any building or structure;"]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-4-paragraph-1-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["upon the owner or occupier of the land directing him to alter the height or character of any wall, fence, hoarding, tree or hedge thereon so as to cause it to conform with any requirements specified in the notice; or"]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-4-paragraph-1-1-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["upon every owner, occupier or lessee of the land restraining him, either absolutely or subject to such conditions as may be specified in the notice, from permitting any building, wall, fence, hoarding, tree or hedge to be erected or planted on the land."]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}, {"id", "schedule-4-paragraph-1"}], ["(2) There shall be annexed to any notice served under Article 49 a plan showing the land to which the notice relates; and notice of the right of objection shall be given in the notice."]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText LegExtentContainer"}, {"id", "schedule-4-paragraph-2"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "schedule-4-paragraph-2"}], ["2."]}, "  Any restrictions imposed by a notice served under Article 49 shall be registered pursuant to Part X of the Land Registration Act (Northern Ireland) 1970", {"a", [{"class", "LegCommentaryLink"}, {"href", "#commentary-c16868211"}, {"title", "View the commentary text for this item"}, {"id", "reference-c16868211"}], ["F175"]}, " and shall remain in force until the notice is withdrawn by the Department and the registration is cancelled in accordance with the provisions of that Part, and any such restrictions shall, while in force, be binding upon any successor in title to the owner, occupier, or lessee of the land to which they relate.", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"div", [{"class", "LegAnnotations"}], [{"div", [{"class", "LegCommentaryItem"}, {"id", "commentary-c16868211"}], [{"p", [{"class", "LegCommentaryPara"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegCommentaryType"}], [{"a", [{"href", "#reference-c16868211"}, {"title", "Go back to reference for this commentary item"}], ["F175"]}]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegCommentaryText"}], [{"a", [{"class", "LegCitation"}, {"title", "Go to item of legislation"}, {"rel", "cite"}, {"href", "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/apni/1970/18"}], ["1970 c. 18 (N.I.)"]}]}]}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText LegExtentContainer"}, {"id", "schedule-4-paragraph-3"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "schedule-4-paragraph-3"}], ["3."]}, "—(1) If any person upon whom a notice has been served under Article 49 objects to complying with any requirement of the notice or objects to any restriction imposed thereby, he may, within 21 days of receiving the notice, give notice in writing to the Department stating his objection and the grounds thereof and requiring the matter in dispute to be heard and determined by a barrister or solicitor of not less than 10 years' standing, practising in Northern Ireland, to be appointed by the Lord Chief Justice.", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}, {"id", "schedule-4-paragraph-3"}], ["(2) A person so appointed shall for the purpose of such hearing have all the powers conferred on an arbitrator by", {"span", [{"class", "LegChangeDelimiter"}], ["["]}, {"a", [{"class", "LegCommentaryLink"}, {"href", "#commentary-c16868221"}, {"title", "View the commentary text for this item"}, {"id", "reference-c16868221"}], ["F176"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegAddition"}], [" Part I of the Arbitation Act 1996"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegChangeDelimiter"}], ["]"]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}, {"id", "schedule-4-paragraph-3"}], ["(3) In determining any question whether a notice shall be withdrawn as respects a requirement or restriction objected to, the arbitrator shall have power to order that the requirement or restriction shall have effect subject to such modifications (if any) as the arbitrator may direct."]}, {"div", [{"class", "LegAnnotations"}], [{"div", [{"class", "LegCommentaryItem"}, {"id", "commentary-c16868221"}], [{"p", [{"class", "LegCommentaryPara"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegCommentaryType"}], [{"a", [{"href", "#reference-c16868221"}, {"title", "Go back to reference for this commentary item"}], ["F176"]}]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegCommentaryText"}], [{"a", [{"class", "LegCitation"}, {"title", "Go to item of legislation"}, {"rel", "cite"}, {"href", "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ukpga/1996/23"}], ["1996 c.23"]}]}]}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText LegExtentContainer"}, {"id", "schedule-4-paragraph-4"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "schedule-4-paragraph-4"}], ["4."]}, "  Any person upon whom a notice is served under Article 49 shall have power, notwithstanding anything in any conveyance or in any lease or other instrument or agreement, to do all such things as may be necessary for complying with the requirements of the notice.", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText LegExtentContainer"}, {"id", "schedule-4-paragraph-5"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "schedule-4-paragraph-5"}], ["5."]}, "—(1) Where notice has been served upon any person under Article 49 the Department may, with the consent of that person, do on his behalf anything necessary for complying with the requirements of the notice.", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}, {"id", "schedule-4-paragraph-5"}], ["(2) Where any such person, within 21 days after the service upon him of the notice, signifies in writing to the Department his assent to the doing by the Department on his behalf of any such thing as aforesaid, such person shall not be liable to prosecution for an offence under paragraph 6."]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText LegExtentContainer"}, {"id", "schedule-4-paragraph-6"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "schedule-4-paragraph-6"}], ["6."]}, "  Subject to the provisions of this Schedule, if any person upon whom a notice has been served under Article 49 contravenes the notice, he shall, without prejudice to any other proceedings which may be taken against him, be guilty of an offence and liable on summary conviction to a fine not exceeding level 3 on the standard scale.", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText LegExtentContainer"}, {"id", "schedule-4-paragraph-7"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "schedule-4-paragraph-7"}], ["7."]}, "  Where a person convicted of an offence under paragraph 6 continues to contravene the notice after the end of such period beginning on the date of that conviction as may be specified by the court—", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-4-paragraph-7-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["he shall be guilty of a further offence and liable on summary conviction to a fine not exceeding one-tenth of level 3 on the standard scale for each day following the end of that period on which the contravention continues; and"]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-4-paragraph-7-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the Department may do anything necessary for complying with the requirements of the notice."]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText LegExtentContainer"}, {"id", "schedule-4-paragraph-8"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "schedule-4-paragraph-8"}], ["8."]}, "—(1) Any person upon whom a notice is served under Article 49 shall be entitled to recover from the Department any expenses reasonably incurred by him in carrying out any directions contained in the notice.", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}, {"id", "schedule-4-paragraph-8"}], ["(2) Any persons sustaining loss in direct consequence of any requirement of a notice served under Article 49, or any person who proves that his property is injuriously affected by restrictions imposed by any such notice, shall, if he makes a claim within six months after the service of the notice, be entitled to recover from the Department compensation for the loss or injury sustained."]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}, {"id", "schedule-4-paragraph-8"}], ["(3) If any question arises whether compensation is payable under this provision, or as to the amount of any compensation so payable, the question shall be referred to and determined by the Lands Tribunal."]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText LegExtentContainer"}, {"id", "schedule-4-paragraph-9"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "schedule-4-paragraph-9"}], ["9."]}, "  Nothing in Article 49 or this Schedule shall apply with respect to any building or other structure belonging to a railway undertaking or to the owners, trustees or conservators acting under powers conferred by any statutory provision of any canal, inland navigation, dock or harbour, where the building or other structure forms part of, or is necessary for the maintenance of, their railway, canal, inland navigation, dock or harbour.", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText LegExtentContainer"}, {"id", "schedule-4-paragraph-10"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "schedule-4-paragraph-10"}], ["10."]}, "  Article 49 and this Schedule shall apply to stacks of turf, hay, corn or other produce, wood piles, wooden sheds and other similar temporary erections in like manner as they apply to a fence or hedge.", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"a", [{"class", "LegAnchorID"}, {"id", "schedule-5"}], []}, {"div", [{"class", "LegClearSchedule"}], []}, {"p", [{"class", "LegArticleRef"}], ["Article 69(5)."]}, {"h2", [{"class", "LegSchedule"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegScheduleNo LegHeadingRef"}], ["SCHEDULE 5", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegTitleBlockTitle"}], ["PROCEDURE FOR MAKING ORDERS UNDER ARTICLE 69(1)"]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText LegExtentContainer"}, {"id", "schedule-5-paragraph-1"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "schedule-5-paragraph-1"}], ["1."]}, "  Where the Department proposes to make an order under Article 69(1), it shall publish in at least one newspaper circulating in the area in which the land is situated a notice—", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-5-paragraph-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["stating the general effect of the proposed order;"]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-5-paragraph-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["specifying a place in that area where a copy of a draft of the order and of any relevant map or plan may be inspected by any person free of charge at all reasonable hours during a period of not less than 30 days from the date of the last publication of the notice;"]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-5-paragraph-1-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["stating that, within that period, any person may by notice to the Department inform it of the grounds upon which he objects to the making of the order."]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText LegExtentContainer"}, {"id", "schedule-5-paragraph-2"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "schedule-5-paragraph-2"}], ["2."]}, "—(1) The Department shall, not later than the date on which the notice referred to in paragraph 1 is published, serve a copy thereof together with a copy of a draft of the order and of any relevant map or plan on the owner and the occupier of land affected by the order.", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}, {"id", "schedule-5-paragraph-2"}], ["(2) Where the Department proposes to modify the terms of the draft of the order, the Department shall give and publish, in such manner as appears to it to be appropriate, such additional notices as the Department considers appropriate for informing all persons likely to be adversely affected by the modification."]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText LegExtentContainer"}, {"id", "schedule-5-paragraph-3"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "schedule-5-paragraph-3"}], ["3."]}, "  If it appears to the Department, when preparing an order, that a new means of access to any land is likely to have to be provided by it to take the place of a means of access to be stopped-up under the order, then the Department shall indicate in the map or plan referred to in the order the proposed route of that new means of access, and shall serve on the owner and occupier of the land which will be required for the provision of that new means of access (if different from the owner and occupier referred to in paragraph 2(1)) a copy of the notice and the other documents referred to in paragraph 1(b).", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText LegExtentContainer"}, {"id", "schedule-5-paragraph-4"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "schedule-5-paragraph-4"}], ["4."]}, "  If, before the expiration of the period referred to in paragraph 1(b), the Department receives an objection from any person on whom a copy of the notice is required to be served under paragraph 2(1) or 3 or from any other person appearing to it to be affected, it may cause a local inquiry to be held.", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText LegExtentContainer"}, {"id", "schedule-5-paragraph-5"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "schedule-5-paragraph-5"}], ["5."]}, "  After considering—", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-5-paragraph-5-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["any objections to the proposed order which are not withdrawn;"]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-5-paragraph-5-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["where a local inquiry is held, the report of the person who held it,"]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegText"}], ["the Department may make the order either without modifications or subject to such modifications as it thinks fit.\r"]}, {"a", [{"class", "LegAnchorID"}, {"id", "schedule-6"}], []}, {"div", [{"class", "LegClearSchedule"}], []}, {"p", [{"class", "LegArticleRef"}], ["Article 105(4) and (5)."]}, {"h2", [{"class", "LegSchedule"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegScheduleNo LegHeadingRef"}], ["SCHEDULE 6", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegTitleBlockTitle"}], ["TIDAL WORKS"]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText LegExtentContainer"}, {"id", "schedule-6-paragraph-1"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "schedule-6-paragraph-1"}], ["1."]}, "  Where the Department constructs, alters or extends any tidal work in contravention of paragraph (3) of Article 105 or of any condition imposed under that paragraph, the Secretary of State may by notice in writing require the Department at its own expense to remove the work and to restore the site of the work to the condition in which it was before the contravention.", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText LegExtentContainer"}, {"id", "schedule-6-paragraph-2"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "schedule-6-paragraph-2"}], ["2."]}, "—(1) Where the Department abandons any tidal work, or allows it to fall into disrepair, the Secretary of State may by notice in writing require the Department at its own expense—", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-6-paragraph-2-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["to repair and restore the work;"]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-6-paragraph-2-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["to remove the work and to restore the land on which it is constructed to the condition in which the land was before the work was constructed."]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}, {"id", "schedule-6-paragraph-2"}], ["(2) Where—"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-6-paragraph-2-2-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the Department abandons any work consisting of a tidal work and of other work or allows a work so consisting to fall into disrepair; and"]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-6-paragraph-2-2-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the Secretary of State is satisfied that any part of the work which is not a tidal work is in such a condition as to interfere with or to cause reasonable apprehension that it may interfere with, navigation or public rights over the foreshore;"]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["the Secretary of State may include that part of the work in a notice under sub-paragraph (1).\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText LegExtentContainer"}, {"id", "schedule-6-paragraph-3"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "schedule-6-paragraph-3"}], ["3."]}, "  Where any tidal work constructed by the Department is damaged or decays, the Department shall—", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-6-paragraph-3-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["forthwith notify the Commissioners of Irish Lights;"]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-6-paragraph-3-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["lay down such buoys, exhibit such lights and take such other steps to prevent any danger to navigation, as those Commissioners may specify."]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText LegExtentContainer"}, {"id", "schedule-6-paragraph-4"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "schedule-6-paragraph-4"}], ["4."]}, "—(1) The Secretary of State may cause a survey and examination to be made—", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-6-paragraph-4-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["of any tidal work; and"]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-6-paragraph-4-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["of the land upon which it is proposed to construct any such work."]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}, {"id", "schedule-6-paragraph-4"}], ["(2) The cost of any survey and examination under sub-paragraph (1) shall be met by the Department."]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText LegExtentContainer"}, {"id", "schedule-6-paragraph-5"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "schedule-6-paragraph-5"}], ["5."]}, "—(1) The Department shall, while a tidal work is being constructed, altered or extended—", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-6-paragraph-5-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["exhibit, at or near the work, every night from sunset to sunrise such lights as the Secretary of State may specify;"]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-6-paragraph-5-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["take such steps to prevent any danger to navigation as the Secretary of State may specify."]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}, {"id", "schedule-6-paragraph-5"}], ["(2) The Department shall, in relation to any tidal work, after the work is completed—"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-6-paragraph-5-2-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["exhibit every night from sunset to sunrise such lights as the Commissioners of Irish Lights may specify, at such places as may be so specified;"]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-6-paragraph-5-2-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["take such steps to prevent any danger to navigation as those Commissioners may specify."]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText LegExtentContainer"}, {"id", "schedule-6-paragraph-6"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "schedule-6-paragraph-6"}], ["6."]}, "  It shall be the duty of the Department to comply with any notice served on it under this Schedule.", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title", "Applies to Northern Ireland"}], [{"span", [{"class", "btr"}], []}, "N.I.", {"span", [{"class", "bbl"}], []}, {"span", [{"class", "bbr"}], []}]}]}, {"a", [{"class", "LegAnchorID"}, {"id", "schedule-7"}], []}, {"div", [{"class", "LegClearSchedule"}], []}, {"p", [{"class", "LegArticleRef"}], ["Article 113(2)."]}, {"h2", [{"class", "LegSchedule"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegScheduleNo LegHeadingRef"}], ["SCHEDULE 7", {"span", [{"class", "LegExtentRestriction"}, {"title"